---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Privacy Policy";
const description = "SnapFitLabs Privacy Policy";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>At SnapFitLabs, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your data and your rights regarding your personal information.</p>

  <h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
  <p>We do not collect any personal data from our users. Our app does not require you to provide any personal information, and we do not track your usage or behavior.</p>

  <h2>2. Third-Party Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>Since we do not collect any personal data, we do not share any data with third parties. We do not use any analytics tools, advertising networks, or third-party SDKs that would require data sharing.</p>

  <h2>3. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
  <p>As we do not collect any personal data, there is no data to retain or delete. Your privacy is ensured by our policy of not collecting any data in the first place.</p>

  <h2>4. User Consent and Data Deletion Requests</h2>
  <p>Since we do not collect any personal data, there is no need for you to revoke consent or request data deletion. Your privacy is protected by our commitment to not collecting any data.</p>
</Layout>
